			<a name="statistics"></a>	
			<font class="heading">Other demographic statistics of the district:</font>

			<ol>
			<p align="justify">
			</p><li>Urban population = 64, 4710 (35 %).</li>
			<li>Rural population = 1200224 (65 %).</li>
			<li>Male population = 987390 (53.5 %).</li>
			<li>Female population = 857544 (46.5 %).</li>
			<li>% Literacy (overall) = 69.96.</li>
			<li>Male Literacy = 76.13 %.</li>
			<li>Female Literacy = 62.94 %.</li>
			<li>Urban Literacy = 81.99 %.</li>
			<li>Rural Literacy = 63.34 %.</li>
			<li>Density of Population = 509 per Sq KM</li>
			<li>Sex Ratio: 1000 (M):868 (F). </li>
			<p></p>
			</ol>

